These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, designer, manager
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, japanese
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, sprite
3 different pets are kept: ferret, pony, rat
1. the japanese is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the american##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the designer is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
6. the japanese is the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | dancer        | designer     | manager    |
| Nationality   | japanese      | american     | indonesian |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | sprite | mirinda   |
| Pet     | rat        | pony      | ferret        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, snowboarding, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, august, april
3 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, train
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's birthday is in april is between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is surfing##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person driving the train##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |
| Sport    | snowboarding    | volleyball | surfing |
| Birthday       | august   | april  | september  |
| Pet         | frog      | fish     | goldfish    |
| Transport   | motorbike | train    | ship        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, airplane, trike
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, blood-red, green
There are 3 different nationalities: french, italian, spanish
3 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, rat
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the bird and the person who likes green##2
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
5. the italian is the italian##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Transport         | trike | bus | airplane |
| Color           | green     | blood-red    | aquamarine |
| Nationality   | french      | spanish     | italian |
| Pet           | rat         | lizard      | bird    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, sprite
House: futuristic, modern, ranch-style
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, writing
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, software-developer, social-worker
1. the modern house is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
4. the paramedic is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
6. the ranch-style house is between the social-worker and the futuristic house##2
7. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the software-developer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | cola       | sprite   |
| House          | futuristic   | ranch-style   | modern     |
| Hobby         | singing  | puzzles    | writing  |
| Job   | software-developer | paramedic | social-worker |

