.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, lemon, pomegranate
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, old-henry, bolivar
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, hiking, board-games
1. the person eating asparagus is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person eating asparagus is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person eating asparagus is the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching action movies is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the old-henry-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |
| Food          | asparagus | lemon    | pomegranate  |
| Cigar           | old-henry      | swisher  | bolivar |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | action   | time-travel  |
| Hobby           | skydiving      | hiking | board-games        |

