.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, soy-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, martial-arts, documentary
3 different games are played: canasta, domino, chess
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, rugby, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is the person playing chess##1
3. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
4. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
6. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
8. the person playing canasta is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage   | 7up         | soy-milk      | lemonade   |
| Movie-Genre        | documentary | martial-arts          | spy |
| Game        | canasta         | domino        | chess       |
| Sport      | rugby       | skateboarding | golf       |

