.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, cola
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, paramedic, teacher
There 3 different types of food: apricot, onion, raspberry
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, trike
1. the teacher is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person drinking cola is the person driving the trike##1
6. the teacher is the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Beverage       | cola | juice    | iced-tea |
| Job         | fisherman   | paramedic | teacher     |
| Food         | onion  | raspberry     | apricot        |
| Transport   | trike       | jet-ski   | bus         |

