.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-9::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, october
There 3 different types of food: banana, blueberry, pineapple
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, soul
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, accountant, engineer
1. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the engineer##3
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is the person eating blueberry##1
6. the architect is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |      3      |
| Birthday      | october       | september | january |
| Food          | blueberry  | banana | pineapple   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | soul   | folk        |
| Job     | engineer | accountant    | architect        |

