.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-10::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, daffodil, balloon-flower
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, ebony, pink
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, classical, d&b
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, russian, thai
1. the person who likes pink is on the far left##1
2. the russian is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
3. the russian is the russian##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
5. the fan of classical is the person who growspoppy##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is between the argentine and the russian##2
7. the fan of d&b is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Flower      | balloon-flower     | daffodil | poppy  |
| Color          | pink   | ebony     | mauve  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | blues    | classical |
| Nationality   | argentine | thai     | russian   |

