.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-11::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, fonseca, cain
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, november, january
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, golf, rugby
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person who's birthday is in november is between the cain-smoker and the person who's birthday is in april##2
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Cigar       | cain   | fonseca | tiparillo  |
| Birthday         | january      | november      | april   |
| Sport       | golf      | rugby       | baseball |
| Transport   | quad-bike | trike       | tram     |

