.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, handball, tennis
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, librarian, manager
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, sports
3 different games are played: poker, backgammon, scrabble
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the manager##3
6. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
7. the person watching drama movies is between the engineer and the librarian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Sport          | tennis | skiing | handball |
| Job           | engineer   | manager   | librarian |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | drama     | disaster  |
| Game   | backgammon     | scrabble  | poker   |

