4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the snake is between the canadian and the australian##2
7. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday      | april    | july   | august      |
| Nationality   | canadian | american   | australian |
| Pet           | cat      | snake      | horse      |
| Transport         | trike | helicopter | car      |

