4. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
