3. the person eating potato is on the far left or far right##3
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the freelancer is between the person eating eggplant and the lawyer##2
6. the alhambra-smoker is the lawyer##1
7. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food         | eggplant      | nectarine     | potato |
| Job           | entrepreneur | freelancer | lawyer     |
| Cigar   | aristoff    | cain       | alhambra      |
| Pet           | cat          | frog       | rabbit     |

