5. the cottage house is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
7. the modern house is on the right of the american##1
8. the colonial house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |       3       |
